**********************
*    REQUIREMENTS    *
**********************

To compile, you need:
- g++ and the C++ standard library (with development files)
- Qt4 library (with development files)
- XML++ library (with development files)
- SDL-mixer and SDL-sound libraries (with development files)

**********************
*    INSTRUCTIONS    *
**********************

To compile GM-Assistant, execute the following commands:

./configure
make

Then, to launch GM-Assistant, just type:

./GM-Assistant
